Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.46,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each morning...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:11.18,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}...she covertly disposed of Gunpei's accumulated blood \N in a glass bottle as part of her daily routine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:16.68,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}She carried out this duty every day, \N carefully ensuring her family never took notice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:20.31,Main,Shuichi,0,0,0,,Hey, Naoko! \NCome eat with us! {Stfu I'm tryna dispose of this blood -A} {Stfu they tryina eat -G}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.81,Main,Naoko,0,0,0,,I'll be right there!
