Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:36.71,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since then, in the attic above the closet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.48,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Gunpei's body was stored.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.22,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, Naoko noticed something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:50.75,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she sprayed water onto \N Gunpei's body with a spray bottle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:57.70,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}...inexplicably, \Nhis skin would be temporarily rejuvenated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.56,Main,Naoko,0,0,0,,You look so precious while you sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.27,Main,Naoko,0,0,0,,...Gunpei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.31,Main,Naoko,0,0,0,,I alone, now and forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:10.76,Main,Naoko,0,0,0,,...have to take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.76,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just who was he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:18.28,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had no doubt died\N on that day long ago, and yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:23.04,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I first came to learn of Kamafusa Gunpei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:30.06,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I had already visited the region several times to \Nresearch the legends of the supernatural beings who dwell there. {\i0}{Suggesting "...to research the legends..." or something to that effect. -Starfish} {Should the last part of the sentence be "that dwell there," since presumably they still live in those mountains? -Axel}{Seconding both of these suggestions. - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:37.39,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,As I was sayin', \Nno one's gonna give you a better deal than me, Mr. Kishibe. {Like I says, ain't no one gon' give you a better deal for ya dosh than this li'l product mover here, Mr. K. - Batsu, your friendly neighborhood mountain salesman}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.47,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,You got nothin' to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.35,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.52,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Try convincing me all you like. \N The mountain isn't for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.61,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Come on, you're missing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.42,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.40,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Yes, hello! \NBatsudera speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.86,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}As to how I learned of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:17:00.41,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just so happened to cross paths \N with Osato Naoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.91,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and read her memories with Heaven's Door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:09.09,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}And with a stroke of good luck,\N I learned of this man's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:10.42,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:13.09,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Huh? Hello? \NDamn reception...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.25,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,O-One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.97,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,What in the world are you, Gunpei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:22.22,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I want to see your true form \N with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.48,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.28,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,...what your goal is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:31.23,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,In the attic above the closet in the mansion.\N That's where I'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:35.16,Main,My parents told me not to talk to strangers,0,0,0,,You're Kishibe Rohan, aren't you? \NThe comics artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.57,Main,My parents told me not to talk to strangers,0,0,0,,I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.99,Main,My parents told me not to talk to strangers,0,0,0,,You've been snooping around here lately, \N haven't you? {Snooping as usual, I see. -Axel}{SnooPING AS usual, I see}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:42.87,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Who are you?
