Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:51.75,Main,My parents told me not to talk to strangers,0,0,0,,There's been a lot of creepy people \N around here lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.59,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.39,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.94,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.19,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Why did you suddenly run{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:12.26,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Sh-She's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.24,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Wh-What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.01,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Sh-She couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.70,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.20,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.95,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Now it looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:28.96,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,...I somehow...\N did something to this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:31.63,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.38,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.00,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Could she really be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.76,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:39.34,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Is she Gunpei's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:46.10,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Osato Naoko became pregnant and had a child \N with the corpse in the attic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:49.85,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Mr. Kishibe, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:52.02,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Mr. Kishibe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.25,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:01.62,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Damn! \NShe's trying to haunt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.67,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Heaven's Door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:07.54,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.17,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,The memories of her life \N written inside her body...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.00,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,They're fading away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.21,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Damn, they're going to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:16.13,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Once they're gone, \N she'll never come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.01,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Before that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:22.39,Note,Caption,0,0,0,,Note: I know no one named Kishibe Rohan. \NIf we ever crossed paths, I would be unable to see him. {Added a period. -A}{Removed period. BITCH -J} {PUT THE GOD DAMN PERIOD BACK, FOOL! -G}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.67,Main,My parents told me not to talk to strangers,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.36,Main,My parents told me not to talk to strangers,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.17,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Th-That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:04.93,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Had I been any slower, \N she would have haunted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:09.62,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,It would have meant... my utter ruin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.44,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,What a terrifying creature.\N A moment more, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.36,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Oh! There you are, Mr. Kishibe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.53,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,I'm awfully sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:22.20,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,My boss just gave me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.36,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}never{\i0} going to sell it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.70,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.72,Main,Batsudera,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.39,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the supernatural being\N I was researching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:34.46,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}I dubbed it the Mutsukabe Hill Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.84,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did it emerge?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.71,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps in the distant past?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:41.92,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}It relies on human love \N and spiritual weakness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.84,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}...forcing them to attend to their needs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:49.18,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}...to ensure it will never bear any manual labor, \N responsibility, hardships, or other struggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:54.04,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}A phantom with no purpose \N other than to proliferate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:58.34,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}In truth, it may be more \N accurately described as a living being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:02.38,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}The happiest moment of its life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:05.07,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}...is when it dies in another's presence.{Okay, so to clarify: He's saying that dying in the presence of another IS the thing that brings the creature more happiness than anything, not that it at some point decides "Well. I've peaked. Guess I should die now," and then does so. Dying and latching on to another person is literally what it lives FOR. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:09.49,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,As such, \N these beings could exist elsewhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:14.16,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Thriving by ending their life \N in the presence of another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.42,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Did all that really happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.08,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Seems a bit far-fetched.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:21.51,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ya can't be totally sure it ain't true, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.80,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You ever heard of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:27.51,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Yes. I believe there to be a comparable \Norganism in the Orion constellation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:30.46,Main,Kaigamori,0,0,0,,H-Hey, listen to me! \NYou guys can't just sit he{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:36.02,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,By the way, I've been pondering this for some time, \N but are you really a space alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:41.44,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Yes. I departed the \N Magellanic Clouds to inhabit Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:47.07,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,{\an8}Fuckin' annoying space alien...{Ditto. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:47.07,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,My spaceship is currently on standby 1,500,000 kilometers above Earth. Aboard it...{someone should make a Navy SEAL rant using this instead}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:52.95,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many other Mutsukabe Hill Phantoms\N are out in the world?{\i0}{I recognize that it might seem weird calling them Mutsukabe Hill Phantoms when they wouldn't be on Mutsukabe Hill, but that's the name he chose to gave them. So... Tough luck, this is how it's gotta be! I added "out there in the world" just to clarify that he doesn't specifically suspect that one location to be overrun with creepy spirits. -Starfish} {This pleases my spirit hate boner. -Axel}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.73,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}I suppose it doesn't matter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:59.29,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}Osato Naoko seems to be happy \N in her own way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:01.03,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and I worked out their goal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:06.90,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm neither a journalist nor a scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.24,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I'm just a comics artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:12.51,Main,My parents told me not to talk to strangers,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:18.06,Main,My parents told me not to talk to strangers,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you think I'll marry \N someone wonderful someday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:20.63,Main,Naoko,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you will.{\i0}{not}
